  "is_bundle": false,
  "feature_bullets": [
    "EASY INSTALLATION：This bathtub filter for tub faucets features adjustable Velcro strap that allow seamless installation on most standard faucets without tools or assembly. The flexible Velcro strap adapt to any faucet shape, making it suitable for use at home, in rental properties, or when traveling",
    "ENHANCED BATH WATER PURIFICATION：Uses 8 different filtering media to effectively remove fluoride, chlorine, heavy metals, rust, and other impurities from water. To strengthen water oxygen/minerals, reducing skin dryness, and dandruff, while nourishing nails and hair. Its pH-balancing tech ensures safety for sensitive skin, mothers, infants, and pets",
    "10 STAGES PURIFICATION： This 10 stages bathtub water filter combines vitamin C balls, mineralization balls, and magnetic energy balls, which inject oxygen and beneficial minerals into the water. Thus, your family and children can enjoy a refreshing and pure bathing experience throughout the year",
    "VERSATILE USE： This bath filter for tub universally fits all standard faucets with tool-free installation, purifying hot/cold water year-round Its compact design suits homes, hotels, apartments, and travel, offering spa-quality bathing for health-conscious users",
    "EFFICIENT MAINTENANCE： This bath filter for baby made of durable ABS plastic can purify at least 2500 gallons of water (depending on water quality and frequency of use). Low maintenance and efficient design to protect the skin are ideal choices for families who value health.",
    "PLEASE NOTE: Friction/dust during transportation may result in first-use residues, so rinse the filter before first use. Use moderate water flow to prevent overflow. If overflow persists, please check bathtub compatibility and consider initiating a return request.",
    "Tips：Leaving gaps in the filter material is to ensure that the filter can allow high-pressure and high flow water to pass smoothly, ensuring overflow protection and stable filtration performance.",
    "Warmly Notice：TDS meters measure conductivity to detect charged salts/impurities (e.g., sodium) but not neutral disinfectants like chlorine or chloramine, so TDS meters cannot measure them."
  ],
  "feature_bullets_count": 8,
  "feature_bullets_flat": "Warmly Notice：TDS meters measure conductivity to detect charged salts/impurities (e.g., sodium) but not neutral disinfectants like chlorine or chloramine, so TDS meters cannot measure them. Tips：Leaving gaps in the filter material is to ensure that the filter can allow high-pressure and high flow water to pass smoothly, ensuring overflow protection and stable filtration performance. PLEASE NOTE: Friction/dust during transportation may result in first-use residues, so rinse the filter before first use. Use moderate water flow to prevent overflow. If overflow persists, please check bathtub compatibility and consider initiating a return request. EFFICIENT MAINTENANCE： This bath filter for baby made of durable ABS plastic can purify at least 2500 gallons of water (depending on water quality and frequency of use). Low maintenance and efficient design to protect the skin are ideal choices for families who value health. VERSATILE USE： This bath filter for tub universally fits all standard faucets with tool-free installation, purifying hot/cold water year-round Its compact design suits homes, hotels, apartments, and travel, offering spa-quality bathing for health-conscious users. 10 STAGES PURIFICATION： This 10 stages bathtub water filter combines vitamin C balls, mineralization balls, and magnetic energy balls, which inject oxygen and beneficial minerals into the water. Thus, your family and children can enjoy a refreshing and pure bathing experience throughout the year. ENHANCED BATH WATER PURIFICATION：Uses 8 different filtering media to effectively remove fluoride, chlorine, heavy metals, rust, and other impurities from water. To strengthen water oxygen/minerals, reducing skin dryness, and dandruff, while nourishing nails and hair. Its pH-balancing tech ensures safety for sensitive skin, mothers, infants, and pets. EASY INSTALLATION：This bathtub filter for tub faucets features adjustable Velcro strap that allow seamless installation on most standard faucets without tools or assembly. The flexible Velcro strap adapt to any faucet shape, making it suitable for use at home, in rental properties, or when traveling.",
